thread.title: BRIEF-Qianjiang Yongan Pharmaceutical says capital management firm cuts stake in co to 6.6 pct from 11.2 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Qianjiang Yongan Pharmaceutical says capital management firm cuts stake in co to 6.6 pct from 11.2 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - qianjiang yongan pharmaceutical co ltd

text:
Jan 24 (Reuters) - Qianjiang Yongan Pharmaceutical Co Ltd
* Says a Shenzhen-based capital management firm cut stake in the co to 6.6 percent(13 million shares) from 11.2 percent (21.9 million shares), during the period from Aug. 4, 2017 to Jan. 18, 2018
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/VgA2ay
